telligence, power, money, charm, talent, and so on. But the ones we tend to stay in love with are, in the long run, the ones who do a decent job loving us back.]]  ^aa50e7#{1}":[35,35],"#Scary Close#Highlights####[[The reality is people are impressed with all kinds of things - intelligence, power, money, charm, talent, and so on. But the ones we tend to stay in love with are, in the long run, the ones who do a decent job loving us back.]]  ^aa50e7#{2}":[36,36],"#Scary Close#Highlights####[[The reality is people are impressed with all kinds of things - intelligence, power, money, charm, talent, and so on. But the ones we tend to stay in love with are, in the long run, the ones who do a decent job loving us back.]]  ^aa50e7#{3}":[37,37],"#Scary Close#Highlights####[[The reality is people are impressed with all kinds of things - intelligence, power, money, charm, talent, and so on. But the ones we tend to stay in love with are, in the long run, the ones who do a decent job loving us back.]]  ^aa50e7#{4}":[38,38],"#Scary Close#Highlights####[[The reality is people are impressed with all kinds of things - intelligence, power, money, charm, talent, and so on. But the ones we tend to stay in love with are, in the long run, the ones who do a decent job loving us back.]]  ^aa50e7#{5}":[39,39],"#Scary Close#Highlights####[[The reality is people are impressed with all kinds of things - intelligence, power, money, charm, talent, and so on. But the ones we tend to stay in love with are, in the long run, the ones who do a decent job loving us back.]]  ^aa50e7#{6}":[40,40],"#Scary Close#Highlights####[[The reality is people are impressed with all kinds of things - intelligence, power, money, charm, talent, and so on. But the ones we tend to stay in love with are, in the long run, the ones who do a decent job loving us back.]]  ^aa50e7#{7}":[41,41],"#Scary Close#Highlights####[[The reality is people are impressed with all kinds of things - intelligence, power, money, charm, talent, and so on. But the ones we tend to stay in love with are, in the long run, the ones who do a decent job loving us back.]]  ^aa50e7#{8}":[42,42],"#Scary Close#Highlights####[[God doesn’t give us crying, pooping children because he wants to advance our careers. He gives them to us to create chaos and deter us from investing too much energy in the gluttonous idols of self-absorption.| God doesn’t give us crying, pooping children because he wants to advance our careers. He gives them to us for the same reason he confused language at the Tower of Babel, to create chaos and deter us from investing too much energy in the gluttonous idols of self-absorption.]] ^c09bda":[43,46],"#Scary Close#Highlights####[[God doesn’t give us crying, pooping children because he wants to advance our careers. He gives them to us to create chaos and deter us from investing too much energy in the gluttonous idols of self-absorption.| God doesn’t give us crying, pooping children because he wants to advance our careers. He gives them to us for the same reason he confused language at the Tower of Babel, to create chaos and deter us from investing too much energy in the gluttonous idols of self-absorption.]] ^c09bda#{1}":[45,45],"#Scary Close#Highlights####[[God doesn’t give us crying, pooping children because he wants to advance our careers. He gives them to us to create chaos and deter us from investing too much energy in the gluttonous idols of self-absorption.| God doesn’t give us crying, pooping children because he wants to advance our careers. He gives them to us for the same reason he confused language at the Tower of Babel, to create chaos and deter us from investing too much energy in the gluttonous idols of self-absorption.]] ^c09bda#{2}":[46,46],"#Scary Close#Highlights####[[Loving a Woman is scarier than climbing a mountain or sailing an ocean. Dead or alive, you’re still a man. A woman, though, can rob your manhood and reduce you to a boy at the drop of a word. It’s no wonder we all try to control each other.| I don't know why loving a woman is scarier than climbing a mountain or sailing an ocean, but it is. A mountain can hurt your body and an ocean can drown you, but in the end you’re still a man for conquering them. Dead or alive, you’re still a man. A woman, though, can rob your manhood and reduce you to a boy at the drop of a word. It’s no wonder we all try to control each other.]]":[47,49],"#Scary Close#Highlights####[[Loving a Woman is scarier than climbing a mountain or sailing an ocean. Dead or alive, you’re still a man. A woman, though, can rob your manhood and reduce you to a boy at the drop of a word. It’s no wonder we all try to control each other.| I don't know why loving a woman is scarier than climbing a mountain or sailing an ocean, but it is. A mountain can hurt your body and an ocean can drown you, but in the end you’re still a man for conquering them. Dead or alive, you’re still a man. A woman, though, can rob your manhood and reduce you to a boy at the drop of a word. It’s no wonder we all try to control each other.]]#{1}":[49,49],"#Scary Close#Highlights####[[When you are conquering world you are rewarded for staying in control. You have to let go in order to gain intimacy.]]":[50,81],"#Scary Close#Highlights####[[When you are conquering world you are rewarded for staying in control. You have to let go in order to gain intimacy.]]#{1}":[52,52],"#Scary Close#Highlights####[[When you are conquering world you are rewarded for staying in control. You have to let go in order to gain intimacy.]]#{2}":[53,53],"#Scary Close#Highlights####[[When you are conquering world you are rewarded for staying in control. You have to let go in order to gain intimacy.]]#{3}":[54,54],"#Scary Close#Highlights####[[When you are conquering world you are rewarded for staying in control. You have to let go in order to gain intimacy.]]#{4}":[55,55],"#Scary Close#Highlights####[[When you are conquering world you are rewarded for staying in control. You 