. You have to let go in order to gain intimacy.]]#{27}":[78,78],"#Scary Close#Highlights####[[When you are conquering world you are rewarded for staying in control. You have to let go in order to gain intimacy.]]#{28}":[79,79],"#Scary Close#Highlights####[[When you are conquering world you are rewarded for staying in control. You have to let go in order to gain intimacy.]]#{29}":[80,80],"#Scary Close#Highlights####[[When you are conquering world you are rewarded for staying in control. You have to let go in order to gain intimacy.]]#{30}":[81,81],"#Scary Close#Highlights####[[Life does seem like a game of poker. There’s all this acceptance and power and love in the middle, and we’re all holding our cards close to our chest trying to win it. It feels like the dumbest thing to do would be to show our cards.|In ways, life really does seem like a game of poker. There’s all this acceptance and power and love in the middle of the table, and we’re all holding our cards close to our chest trying to win it. It feels like the dumbest thing to do would be to show our cards.]]":[82,86],"#Scary Close#Highlights####[[Life does seem like a game of poker. There’s all this acceptance and power and love in the middle, and we’re all holding our cards close to our chest trying to win it. It feels like the dumbest thing to do would be to show our cards.|In ways, life really does seem like a game of poker. There’s all this acceptance and power and love in the middle of the table, and we’re all holding our cards close to our chest trying to win it. It feels like the dumbest thing to do would be to show our cards.]]#{1}":[84,84],"#Scary Close#Highlights####[[Life does seem like a game of poker. There’s all this acceptance and power and love in the middle, and we’re all holding our cards close to our chest trying to win it. It feels like the dumbest thing to do would be to show our cards.|In ways, life really does seem like a game of poker. There’s all this acceptance and power and love in the middle of the table, and we’re all holding our cards close to our chest trying to win it. It feels like the dumbest thing to do would be to show our cards.]]#{2}":[85,86],"#Scary Close#Highlights####[[No matter what they told me, I wouldn’t judge them. That I wouldn’t make them feel like lesser people for their mistakes. And because of that, they learned to trust me with their deepest thoughts.”|it was this single decision I made early on: I decided I wouldn’t judge my kids. No matter what they told me, I wouldn’t judge them. I might have to discipline them, but I wouldn’t make them feel like lesser people for their mistakes. And because of that, they learned to trust me with their deepest thoughts. ]]":[87,96],"#Scary Close#Highlights####[[No matter what they told me, I wouldn’t judge them. That I wouldn’t make them feel like lesser people for their mistakes. And because of that, they learned to trust me with their deepest thoughts.”|it was this single decision I made early on: I decided I wouldn’t judge my kids. No matter what they told me, I wouldn’t judge them. I might have to discipline them, but I wouldn’t make them feel like lesser people for their mistakes. And because of that, they learned to trust me with their deepest thoughts. ]]#{1}":[89,89],"#Scary Close#Highlights####[[No matter what they told me, I wouldn’t judge them. That I wouldn’t make them feel like lesser people for their mistakes. And because of that, they learned to trust me with their deepest thoughts.”|it was this single decision I made early on: I decided I wouldn’t judge my kids. No matter what they told me, I wouldn’t judge them. I might have to discipline them, but I wouldn’t make them feel like lesser people for their mistakes. And because of that, they learned to trust me with their deepest thoughts. ]]#{2}":[90,90],"#Scary Close#Highlights####[[No matter what they told me, I wouldn’t judge them. That I wouldn’t make them feel like lesser people for their mistakes. And because of 