he long run, the ones who do a decent job loving us back.","line":33},{"title":"Location 857","target":"https://readwise.io/to_kindle?action=open&asin=B00KQ2G45W&location=857","line":35},{"title":"Location 868","target":"https://readwise.io/to_kindle?action=open&asin=B00KQ2G45W&location=868","line":36},{"title":"Location 875","target":"https://readwise.io/to_kindle?action=open&asin=B00KQ2G45W&location=875","line":37},{"title":"Location 905","target":"https://readwise.io/to_kindle?action=open&asin=B00KQ2G45W&location=905","line":38},{"title":"Location 976","target":"https://readwise.io/to_kindle?action=open&asin=B00KQ2G45W&location=976","line":39},{"title":"Location 991","target":"https://readwise.io/to_kindle?action=open&asin=B00KQ2G45W&location=991","line":40},{"title":"Location 1022","target":"https://readwise.io/to_kindle?action=open&asin=B00KQ2G45W&location=1022","line":41},{"title":"Location 1040","target":"https://readwise.io/to_kindle?action=open&asin=B00KQ2G45W&location=1040","line":42},{"title":" God doesn’t give us crying, pooping children because he wants to advance our careers. He gives them to us for the same reason he confused language at the Tower of Babel, to create chaos and deter us from investing too much energy in the gluttonous idols of self-absorption.","target":"God doesn’t give us crying, pooping children because he wants to advance our careers. He gives them to us to create chaos and deter us from investing too much energy in the gluttonous idols of self-absorption.","line":43},{"title":"Location 1059","target":"https://readwise.io/to_kindle?action=open&asin=B00KQ2G45W&location=1059","line":45},{"title":"Location 1132","target":"https://readwise.io/to_kindle?action=open&asin=B00KQ2G45W&location=1132","line":46},{"title":" I don't know why loving a woman is scarier than climbing a mountain or sailing an ocean, but it is. A mountain can hurt your body and an ocean can drown you, but in the end you’re still a man for conquering them. Dead or alive, you’re still a man. A woman, though, can rob your manhood and reduce you to a boy at the drop of a word. It’s no wonder we all try to control each other.","target":"Loving a Woman is scarier than climbing a mountain or sailing an ocean. Dead or alive, you’re still a man. A woman, though, can rob your manhood and reduce you to a boy at the drop of a word. It’s no wonder we all try to control each other.","line":47},{"title":"Location 1137","target":"https://readwise.io/to_kindle?action=open&asin=B00KQ2G45W&location=1137","line":49},{"title":"When you are conquering world you are rewarded for staying in control. You have to let go in order to gain intimacy.","target":"When you are conquering world you are rewarded for staying in control. You have to let go in order to gain intimacy.","line":50},{"title":"Location 1197","target":"https://readwise.io/to_kindle?action=open&asin=B00KQ2G45W&location=1197","line":52},{"title":"Location 1203","target":"https://readwise.io/to_kindle?action=open&asin=B00KQ2G45W&location=1203","line":53},{"title":"Location 1220","target":"https://readwise.io/to_kindle?action=open&asin=B00KQ2G45W&location=1220","line":54},{"title":"Location 1221","target":"https://readwise.io/to_kindle?action=open&asin=B00KQ2G45W&location=1221","line":55},{"title":"Location 1223","target":"https://readwise.io/to_kindle?action=open&asin=B00KQ2G45W&location=1223","line":56},{"title":"Location 1238","target":"https://readwise.io/to_kindle?action=open&asin=B00KQ2G45W&location=1238","line":57},{"title":"Location 1257","target":"https://readwise.io/to_kindle?action=open&asin=B00KQ2G45W&location=1257","line":58},{"title":"Location 1261","target":"https://readwise.io/to_kindle?action=open&asin=B00KQ2G45W&location=1261","line":59},{"title":"Location 1272","target":"https://readwise.io/to_kindle?action=open&asin=B00KQ2G45W&location=1272","line":60},{"title":"Location 1312","target":"https://readwise.io/to_kindle?action=open&asin=B00KQ2G45W&location=1312","line":61},{