 around us.","target":"We will never feel loved until we drop the act, until we’re willing to show our true selves to the people around us.","line":13},{"title":"Location 206","target":"https://readwise.io/to_kindle?action=open&asin=B00KQ2G45W&location=206","line":15},{"title":"Location 209","target":"https://readwise.io/to_kindle?action=open&asin=B00KQ2G45W&location=209","line":16},{"title":"Location 232","target":"https://readwise.io/to_kindle?action=open&asin=B00KQ2G45W&location=232","line":17},{"title":"Location 234","target":"https://readwise.io/to_kindle?action=open&asin=B00KQ2G45W&location=234","line":18},{"title":"Location 234","target":"https://readwise.io/to_kindle?action=open&asin=B00KQ2G45W&location=234","line":19},{"title":"Location 267","target":"https://readwise.io/to_kindle?action=open&asin=B00KQ2G45W&location=267","line":20},{"title":"Location 336","target":"https://readwise.io/to_kindle?action=open&asin=B00KQ2G45W&location=336","line":21},{"title":"Location 406","target":"https://readwise.io/to_kindle?action=open&asin=B00KQ2G45W&location=406","line":22},{"title":"Location 548","target":"https://readwise.io/to_kindle?action=open&asin=B00KQ2G45W&location=548","line":23},{"title":"Location 580","target":"https://readwise.io/to_kindle?action=open&asin=B00KQ2G45W&location=580","line":24},{"title":"Location 585","target":"https://readwise.io/to_kindle?action=open&asin=B00KQ2G45W&location=585","line":25},{"title":"Location 605","target":"https://readwise.io/to_kindle?action=open&asin=B00KQ2G45W&location=605","line":26},{"title":"Location 620","target":"https://readwise.io/to_kindle?action=open&asin=B00KQ2G45W&location=620","line":27},{"title":"Location 654","target":"https://readwise.io/to_kindle?action=open&asin=B00KQ2G45W&location=654","line":28},{"title":"Location 657","target":"https://readwise.io/to_kindle?action=open&asin=B00KQ2G45W&location=657","line":29},{"title":"Location 819","target":"https://readwise.io/to_kindle?action=open&asin=B00KQ2G45W&location=819","line":30},{"title":"Location 823","target":"https://readwise.io/to_kindle?action=open&asin=B00KQ2G45W&location=823","line":31},{"title":"The reality is people are impressed with all kinds of things - intelligence, power, money, charm, talent, and so on. But the ones we tend to stay in love with are, in the long run, the ones who do a decent job loving us back.","target":"The reality is people are impressed with all kinds of things - intelligence, power, money, charm, talent, and so on. But the ones we tend to stay in love with are, in the long run, the ones who do a decent job loving us back.","line":33},{"title":"Location 857","target":"https://readwise.io/to_kindle?action=open&asin=B00KQ2G45W&location=857","line":35},{"title":"Location 868","target":"https://readwise.io/to_kindle?action=open&asin=B00KQ2G45W&location=868","line":36},{"title":"Location 875","target":"https://readwise.io/to_kindle?action=open&asin=B00KQ2G45W&location=875","line":37},{"title":"Location 905","target":"https://readwise.io/to_kindle?action=open&asin=B00KQ2G45W&location=905","line":38},{"title":"Location 976","target":"https://readwise.io/to_kindle?action=open&asin=B00KQ2G45W&location=976","line":39},{"title":"Location 991","target":"https://readwise.io/to_kindle?action=open&asin=B00KQ2G45W&location=991","line":40},{"title":"Location 1022","target":"https://readwise.io/to_kindle?action=open&asin=B00KQ2G45W&location=1022","line":41},{"title":"Location 1040","target":"https://readwise.io/to_kindle?action=open&asin=B00KQ2G45W&location=1040","line":42},{"title":" God doesn’t give us crying, pooping children because he wants to advance our careers. He gives them to us for the same reason he confused language at the Tower of Babel, to create chaos and deter us from investing too much energy in the gluttonous idols of self-absorption.","target":"God doesn’t give us crying, pooping children because he wants to advance our careers. He gives them to us to create chaos and deter us from investing too much energy in the gluttonous idols of self-absorption.","line":43},{"title":"Location 1059","target":"https://readwise.io/to_kindle?action=open&asin=B00KQ2G45W&location=1059","line":45},{"title":"Location 1132","target":"https://readwise.io/to_kindle?action=open&asin=B00KQ2G45W&location=1132","line":46},{"title":" I don't know why loving a woman is scarier than climbing a mountain or sailing an ocean, but it is. A mountain can hurt your body and an ocean can drown you, but in the end you’re still a man for conquering them. Dead or alive, you’re still a man. A woman, though, can rob your manhood and reduce you to a boy at the drop of a word. It’s no wonder we all try to control each other.","target":"Loving a Woman is scarier than climbing a mountain or sailing an ocean. Dead or alive, you’re still a man. A woman, though, can rob your manhood and reduce you to a boy at the drop of a word. It’s no wonder we all try to control each other.","line":47},{"title":"Location 1137","target":"https://readwise.io/to_kindle?action=open&asin=B00KQ2G45W&location=1137","line":49},{"title":"When you are conquering world you are rewarded for staying in control. You have to let go in order to gain intimacy.","target":"When you are conquering world you are rewarded for staying in control. You have to let go in order to gain intimacy.","line":50},{"title":"Location 1197","target":"https://readwise.io/to_kindle?action=open&asin=B00KQ2G45W&location=1197","line":52},{"title":"Location 1203","target":"https://readwise.io/to_kindle?action=open&asin=B00KQ2G45W&location=1203","line":53},{"title":"Location 1220","target":"https://readwise.io/to_kindle?action=open&asin=B00KQ2G45W&location=1220","line":54},{"title":"Location 1221","target":"https://readwise.io/to_kindle?action=open&asin=B00KQ2G45W&location=1221","line":55},{"title":"Location 1223","target":"https://readwise.io/to_kindle?action=open&asin=B00KQ2G45W&location=1223","line":56},{"title":"Location 1238","target":"https://readwise.io/to_kindle?action=open&asin=B00KQ2G45W&location=1238","line":57},{"title":"Location 1257","target":"https://readwise.io/to_kindle?action=open&asin=B00KQ2G45W&location=1257","line":58},{"title":"Location 1261","target":"https://readwise.io/to_kindle?action=open&asin=B00KQ2G45W&location=1261","line":59},{"title":"Location 1272","target":"https://readwise.io/to_kindle?action=open&asin=B00KQ2G45W&location=1272","line":60},{"title":"Location 1312","target":"https://readwise.io/to_kindle?action=open&asin=B00KQ2G45W&location=1312","line":61},{"title":"Location 1421","target":"https://readwise.io/to_kindle?action=open&asin=B00KQ2G45W&location=1421","line":62},{"title":"Location 1429","target":"https://readwise.io/to_kindle?action=open&asin=B00KQ2G45W&location=1429","line":63},{"title":"Location 1451","target":"https://readwise.io/to_kindle?action=open&asin=B00KQ2G45W&location=1451","line":64},{"title":"Location 1452","target":"https://readwise.io/to_kindle?action=open&asin=B00KQ2G45W&location=1452","line":65},{"title":"Location 1547","target":"https://readwise.io/to_kindle?action=open&asin=B00KQ2G45W&location=1547","line":66},{"title":"Location 1561","target":"https://readwise.io/to_kindle?action=open&asin=B00KQ2G45W&location=1561","line":67},{"title":"Location 1564","target":"https://readwise.io/to_kindle?action=open&asin=B00KQ2G45W&location=1564","line":68},{"title":"Location 1588","target":"https://readwise.io/to_kindle?action=open&asin=B00KQ2G45W&location=1588","line":69},{"title":"Location 1589","target":"https://readwise.io/to_kindle?action=open&asin=B00KQ2G45W&location=1589","line":70},{"title":"Location 1620","target":"https://readwise.io/to_kindle?action=open&asin=B00KQ2G45W&location=1620","line":71},{"title":"Location 1629","target":"https://readwise.io/to_kindle?action=open&asin=B00KQ2G45W&location=1629","line":72},{"title":"Location 1635","target":"https://readwise.io/to_kindle?action=open&asin=B00KQ2G45W&location=1635","line":73},{"title":"Location 1644","target":"https://readwise.io/to_kindle?action=open&asin=B00KQ2G45W&location=1644","line":74},{"title":"Location 1650","target":"https://readwise.io/to_kindle?action=open&asin=B00KQ2G45W&location=1650","line":75},{"title":"Location 1660","target":"https://readwise.io/to_kindle?action=open&asin=B00KQ2G45W&location=1660","line":76},{"title":"Location 1673","target":"https://readwise.io/to_kindle?action=open&asin=B00KQ2G45W&location=1673","line":77},{"title":"Location 1688","target":"https://readwise.io/to_kindle?action=open&asin=B00KQ2G45W&location=1688","line":78},{"title":"Location 1697","target":"https://readwise.io/to_kindle?action=open&asin=B00KQ2G45W&location=1697","line":79},{"title":"Location 1721","target":"https://readwise.io/to_kindle?action=open&asin=B00KQ2G45W&location=1721","line":80},{"title":"Location 1768","target":"https://readwise.io/to_kindle?action=open&asin=B00KQ2G45W&location=1768","line":81},{"title":"In ways, life really does seem like a game of poker. There’s all this acceptance and power and love in the middle of the table, and we’re all holding our cards close to our chest trying to win it. It feels like the dumbest thing to do would be to show our cards.","target":"Life does seem like a game of poker. There’s all this acceptance and power and love in the middle, and we’re all holding our cards close to our chest trying to win it. It feels like the dumbest thing to do would be to show our cards.","line":82},{"title":"Location 1816","target":"https://readwise.io/to_kindle?action=open&asin=B00KQ2G45W&location=1816","line":84},{"title":"Location 1831","target":"https://readwise.io/to_kindle?action=open&asin=B00KQ2G45W&location=1831","line":85},{"title":"it was this single decision I made early on: I decided I wouldn’t judge my kids. No matter what they told me, I wouldn’t judge them. I might have to discipline them, but I wouldn’t make them feel like lesser people for their mistakes. And because of that, they learned to trust me with their deepest thoughts. ","target":"No matter what they told me, I wouldn’t judge them. That I wouldn’t make them feel like lesser people for their mistakes. And because of that, they learned to trust me with their deepest thoughts.”","line":87},{"title":"Location 1848","target":"https://readwise.io/to_kindle?action=open&asin=B00KQ2G45W&location=1848","line":89},{"title":"Location 1854","target":"https://readwise.io/to_kindle?action=open&asin=B00KQ2G45W&location=1854","line":90},{"title":"Location 1864","target":"https://readwise.io/to_kindle?action=open&asin=B00KQ2G45W&location=1864","line":91},{"title":"Location 1874","target":"https://readwise.io/to_kindle?action=open&asin=B00KQ2G45W&location=1874","line":92},{"title":"Location 1879","target":"https://readwise.io/to_kindle?action=open&asin=B00KQ2G45W&location=1879","line":93},{"title":"Location 1929","target":"https://readwise.io/to_kindle?action=open&asin=B00KQ2G45W&location=1929","line":94},{"title":"Location 1982","target":"https://readwise.io/to_kindle?action=open&asin=B00KQ2G45W&location=1982","line":95},{"title":"Location 1988","target":"https://readwise.io/to_kindle?action=open&asin=B00KQ2G45W&location=1988","line":96},{"title":"“Men move toward whatever makes them feel competent.”","target":"“Men move toward whatever makes them feel competent.”","line":97},{"title":"Location 2102","target":"https://readwise.io/to_kindle?action=open&asin=B00KQ2G45W&location=2102","line":100},{"title":"Location 2121","target":"https://readwise.io/to_kindle?action=open&asin=B00KQ2G45W&location=2121","line":101},{"title":"Location 2124","target":"https://readwise.io/to_kindle?action=open&asin=B00KQ2G45W&location=2124","line":102},{"title":"Location 2190","target":"https://readwise.io/to_kindle?action=open&asin=B00KQ2G45W&location=2190","line":103},{"title":"Location 2203","target":"https://readwise.io/to_kindle?action=open&asin=B00KQ2G45W&location=2203","line":104},{"title":"Location 2224","target":"https://readwise.io/to_kind