"smart_blocks:_007.Books/Scary Close/Scary Close 📕.md#Scary Close#Highlights####[[Loving a Woman is scarier than climbing a mountain or sailing an ocean. Dead or alive, you’re still a man. A woman, though, can rob your manhood and reduce you to a boy at the drop of a word. It’s no wonder we all try to control each other.| I don't know why loving a woman is scarier than climbing a mountain or sailing an ocean, but it is. A mountain can hurt your body and an ocean can drown you, but in the end you’re still a man for conquering them. Dead or alive, you’re still a man. A woman, though, can rob your manhood and reduce you to a boy at the drop of a word. It’s no wonder we all try to control each other.]]": {"path":null,"embeddings":{"TaylorAI/bge-micro-v2":{"vec":[-0.05929932,0.02466729,0.00049577,0.06477575,-0.00760638,0.015562,0.07831354,0.02446479,0.01693971,-0.06282617,0.00892095,-0.05763642,0.03005326,0.05751857,0.02818896,0.08205039,-0.01381013,0.07884016,-0.10775163,0.08139026,0.03610039,0.03663909,0.03244947,-0.01499024,0.03608193,-0.01757159,-0.05845767,-0.0506485,-0.06969779,-0.14254408,-0.03177509,-0.0061044,-0.02482768,-0.03447612,0.02001236,-0.00365848,-0.01830507,-0.01373854,-0.04108995,0.03608589,0.04062612,0.01586471,0.02653857,0.00246525,-0.01209787,0.04644604,-0.02150715,0.00053308,0.03655983,-0.08129544,-0.06155356,-0.06799313,-0.0631221,0.0277003,-0.00718232,-0.03656754,0.02996452,0.00267246,-0.04107527,0.06731642,0.06504573,-0.01258971,-0.1401836,0.06868561,0.02235516,-0.00414119,-0.05041323,0.01934688,0.05550541,0.06577408,-0.05815146,0.04072868,-0.05249174,0.03756279,0.02380927,-0.03996385,0.01896406,-0.06572229,-0.01691155,0.02765513,-0.04681209,-0.0494832,-0.01731982,-0.03693439,-0.00135632,-0.00095795,0.08041463,-0.03758091,-0.00202126,0.02354585,0.00473011,-0.01168729,0.05637203,0.04511651,-0.04880776,-0.0357141,0.04176763,-0.00324399,-0.09669527,0.12928809,-0.05777802,0.01683572,-0.03443222,-0.00046885,0.03565652,-0.01071441,0.05243797,0.022047