"smart_blocks:_007.Books/Scary Close/Scary Close 📕.md#Scary Close#Highlights####[[Life does seem like a game of poker. There’s all this acceptance and power and love in the middle, and we’re all holding our cards close to our chest trying to win it. It feels like the dumbest thing to do would be to show our cards.|In ways, life really does seem like a game of poker. There’s all this acceptance and power and love in the middle of the table, and we’re all holding our cards close to our chest trying to win it. It feels like the dumbest thing to do would be to show our cards.]]": {"path":null,"embeddings":{"TaylorAI/bge-micro-v2":{"vec":[-0.02315758,0.02805005,-0.02220603,-0.00184734,0.01433669,0.02986599,0.07123468,-0.00807821,0.05608855,-0.06122098,-0.01663212,-0.04878259,-0.00189486,0.03151042,-0.01677761,0.03615202,-0.01595134,-0.03483138,-0.09949498,0.11016657,0.0008216,0.03091587,0.0229389,-0.02694337,0.05954426,0.00542671,-0.01330331,-0.06842483,-0.06753065,-0.15578569,0.02080333,0.03090152,-0.0090634,-0.01291134,0.01043252,-0.0757943,-0.05070638,0.02987326,-0.05865257,0.02447336,0.04471383,0.02831368,0.01123344,0.01551105,0.01619883,-0.01618256,-0.00599951,-0.01318561,0.04155068,-0.05558594,-0.06529438,0.02565389,0.01655176,-0.00570217,-0.00634247,0.02556208,0.09190639,0.00032625,-0.00870788,0.05863277,0.07570948,0.04356771,-0.13864408,0.09371051,-0.0024854,-0.03074418,-0.03427603,0.05290199,0.04009957,0.07886103,-0.00584864,0.02547184,-0.01127511,0.03802788,0.03483716,-0.02216972,-0.01088747,-0.05868068,0.01441308,-0.00661357,-0.03994762,-0.01005745,0.02858523,-0.04628493,-0.06047986,0.01053219,0.07716813,-0.02986529,-0.02253349,0.01691779,0.00664996,0.00099537,-0.01201359,0.0121268,-0.0401229,-0.02067108,0.02947598,-0.01179829,-0.07927967,0.09102824,-0.03631761,0.03733764,0.02041547,-0.02440631,0.02649154,0.03041439,0.01127928,-0.05264759,-0.04478842,-0.03658873,0.00356069,-0.05610555,0.0458003,-0.0631572,0.09525315,0.02308285,0.02895064,0.01217557,0.01959082,